-Are you the father?

22:37.320 --> 22:40.240
-Yes.
-Your son has a bad case of viral croup.

22:40.960 --> 22:42.240
Sorry. Is that serious?

22:42.320 --> 22:46.600
The respiratory tract is inflamed,
which is hindering his breathing.

22:46.680 --> 22:47.560
Okay, yes.

22:47.640 --> 22:50.000
We'll keep him here overnight
for observation.

22:50.600 --> 22:51.680
Yes.

22:51.760 --> 22:55.280
Hey, boy. Hey.

22:59.200 --> 23:00.720
<i>Could Constance and I go private?</i>

23:00.800 --> 23:04.920
Yes. If you want, I can let you go private
so the two of you can talk one-on-one.

23:06.240 --> 23:08.320
-Do you want that too, Marion?
-<i>Yes, great.</i>

23:08.400 --> 23:10.200
Okay, I'll let you go private now.

23:11.880 --> 23:15.520
The deal was that we wouldn't listen in
on private conversations,

23:15.600 --> 23:17.080
but we could if we wanted to.

23:18.560 --> 23:22.680
Open relationship.
LAT. Living Apart Together.

23:24.040 --> 23:28.640
Okay, so if I ran into your girlfriend,
I could just tell her we were doing it?

23:28.720 --> 23:30.320
Theoretically speaking.

23:30.400 --> 23:34.480
-No, I wouldn't want to take it that far.
-Okay, I get it.

23:34.560 --> 23:36.320
You just want to have it both ways.

23:37.160 --> 23:40.160
<i>No, it's more</i>
<i>that I don't want to rub it in.</i>

23:41.120 --> 23:44.640
<i>I mean, that would be</i>
<i>kind of humiliating for her.</i>

23:45.160 --> 23:47.360
<i>But yes, in theory…</i>

24:10.400 --> 24:13.040
<i>Hey, I would really like to meet you.</i>

24:13.720 --> 24:17.600
<i>And I… You sound really fun,</i>

24:18.120 --> 24:20.200
