they can say whatever they want.

24:42.360 --> 24:44.160
I blocked a few of them just now.

24:45.520 --> 24:46.760
What?

24:46.840 --> 24:48.280
Oh, great.

24:48.360 --> 24:50.400
The chicks don't get off scot-free either.

24:52.440 --> 24:56.880
Running after those men like tame sheep
just to get a little attention.

24:56.960 --> 24:58.600
Well, I know one of those.

25:00.600 --> 25:04.200
Yeah, I get so sick of myself sometimes,
how I am with Mischa.

25:04.280 --> 25:08.480
Honestly, he comes and goes as he pleases
and I always let him get away with it.

25:10.560 --> 25:14.960
-This is where you tell me we're a great--
-He kissed me. Mischa.

25:18.040 --> 25:18.880
What?

25:20.240 --> 25:21.080
When?

25:22.040 --> 25:25.560
This afternoon.
In the kitchen. Just before we left.

25:25.640 --> 25:28.680
-You see? I thought there was--
-But it was very short.

25:31.520 --> 25:32.360
What happened?

25:32.440 --> 25:34.840
Well, he came out the shower--

25:34.920 --> 25:36.960
So you thought,
"I'll kiss him on the mouth"?

25:37.040 --> 25:38.360
No, of course not, Jan.

25:38.440 --> 25:40.200
I didn't want it, okay?

25:40.280 --> 25:43.160
But, yes, I did let it happen.

25:43.680 --> 25:45.000
And I'm sorry.

25:49.320 --> 25:52.160
-Do you want a relationship with him?
-No, of course not.

25:53.480 --> 25:54.800
That's not even an option.

25:59.520 --> 26:01.600
There's something else I should tell you.

27:00.360 --> 27:02.040
Step it up a notch, Ramon.

27:02.800 --> 27:04.480
Come on. You can do it.

27:19.560 --> 27:21.000
Professor DeWolff?

27:21.720 --> 27:22.560
Leon.

27:23.280 --> 27:24.240
Since when?

27:25.320 --> 27:26.440
It's been a while.

27:28.240 --> 27:29.560
Quite a while.

27:29.640 --> 27:32.440
-Why have you never said anything?
-Well, I don't know.

27:33.320 --> 27:34.640
He's our professor.

27:35.360 --> 27:38.360
What if Eva found out?
He is married after all.

27:40.360 --> 27:41.200
Do you like him?

27:42.360 --> 27:44.120
Well, I…

27:44.640 --> 27:46.200
-It's mostly…
-Sex?

27:49.320 --> 27:51.840
-Oh, my God.
-He loves me.

27:52.920 --> 27:54.000
Oh, shit.

27:54.680 --> 27:56.920
-Does he have kids?
-Twins.

27:58.880 --> 28:01.880
And he loves you. Shit, man.

28:04.960 --> 28:08.040
Just one thing.
You know when Mischa kissed you?

28:10.000 --> 28:12.560
Why didn't you tell me straight away?

28:13.840 --> 28:17.560
I don't know. We've hardly spoken
these past months, Jan.

28:18.080 --> 28:21.320
-I thought you'd blame me.
-Okay, I'm really going to end this.

28:24.320 --> 28:25.520
-Really?
-Yes.

28:31.320 --> 28:32.160
Me too.

28:33.200 --> 28:34.960
It's gone on for way too long.

28:35.480 --> 28:37.160
-Really?
-Yes.

28:38.600 --> 28:39.440
Okay.

28:40.960 --> 28:42.880
I end it with Mischa,
you end it with Leon.

28:48.360 --> 28:49.520
Shall we leave?

28:54.280 --> 28:55.120
Okay.

29:10.560 --> 29:11.800
I need to piss first.

29:26.040 --> 29:26.880
Be careful.

29:30.000 --> 29:30.840
Why?

29:32.040 --> 29:35.560
Julian is part
of the furniture here. Literally.

29:36.720 --> 29:38.920
He's eager and always horny.

29:40.560 --> 29:43.320
-Good.
-Yes, and totally irresponsible.

29:45.280 --> 29:48.520
Let's put it this way. If you walk
out of here with just a cold sore,

29:48.600 --> 29:49.880
then count yourself lucky.

29:50.840 --> 29:53.920
Because of him, half the town
has had swabs up their urethras

29:54.000 --> 29:56.040
at the Community Health Service.

29:57.320 --> 29:58.880
Are you speaking from experience?

30:02.560 --> 30:03.400
Come on.

30:27.000 --> 30:28.480
Are you expecting visitors?

30:29.240 --> 30:30.080
No.

30:54.160 --> 30:55.960
That's Floris.

30:56.600 --> 30:57.440
My partner.

30:58.640 --> 31:00.680
He contracted pneumonia.

31:01.840 --> 31:04.320
It wouldn't go away.
It just kept getting worse,

31:05.520 --> 31:07.360
and then they figured it was cancer.

31:09.680 --> 31:12.040
Well, and later on

31:13.440 --> 31:15.960
when they suspected it might be AIDS,

31:16.040 --> 31:18.040
we hoped it was just cancer.

31:20.680 --> 31:23.760
Less than two months
after that photo, he died.

31:27.160 --> 31:28.240
But I'm clean.

31:50.400 --> 31:52.680
You guys don't need to stay.

31:54.400 --> 31:56.960
-Sorry I called you here for nothing.
-No, not at all.

31:58.120 --> 31:59.960
I'm glad you called.

32:02.520 --> 32:03.640
You got here fast.

32:06.080 --> 32:08.320
-I was still awake.
-Were you at 't Rijk?

32:08.840 --> 32:13.080
Yes, we had to entertain
a business associate.

32:13.160 --> 32:14.320
Poor you.

32:21.120 --> 32:21.960
