32:24.800 --> 32:25.640
Well done.

32:27.400 --> 32:28.440
Hey.

32:30.440 --> 32:35.280
-Sorry, is the Ferrari yours?
-Yes, all 380bhp of it. Want to buy it?

32:35.360 --> 32:38.120
Please, can you move it?
It's blocking the entrance.

32:39.200 --> 32:42.520
Can you take Natas home?
There's no need for you to stay.

32:42.600 --> 32:44.760
Are you sure? It's no trouble at all.

32:44.840 --> 32:45.720
We'll be alright.

32:46.840 --> 32:47.680
Okay.

32:50.120 --> 32:51.600
Hey, Django.

32:54.440 --> 32:56.760
Are you sure? Okay. Call me.

33:05.040 --> 33:05.880
Want to drive?

33:06.800 --> 33:07.880
-Really?
-Yes.

33:10.400 --> 33:11.440
Okay, hit it.

33:19.200 --> 33:20.400
Do you know what?

33:22.640 --> 33:23.480
It feels

33:25.320 --> 33:27.600
