33:28.280 --> 33:29.760
What have you got to lose?

33:34.320 --> 33:35.160
Everything.

33:37.680 --> 33:38.680
My marriage.

33:40.520 --> 33:41.440
My family.

33:43.560 --> 33:44.720
Everything I know.

33:47.400 --> 33:50.400
-The way people see me.
-But there's also something to gain.

33:52.360 --> 33:53.480
What?

33:53.560 --> 33:55.800
Well, something you keep ignoring.

33:56.920 --> 33:58.120
Your greatest good.

33:59.400 --> 34:01.560
-My greatest good?
-Yes.

34:03.720 --> 34:04.880
What's that?

34:05.960 --> 34:06.800
Me.

34:07.600 --> 34:10.440
Well, not me. But you. Your me.

34:11.360 --> 34:12.200
Yourself.

34:16.560 --> 34:19.040
You only see yourself
through other people's eyes.

34:20.600 --> 34:22.240
And you keep conforming to that.

34:23.840 --> 34:28.040
You can keep that up for a long time.
Some people for their entire lives.

34:29.560 --> 34:31.440
You're trying to do everything right.

34:32.760 --> 34:34.360
But it's never good enough.

34:35.400 --> 34:37.240
You seem to know me very well.

34:37.840 --> 34:39.080
You're not the only one.

34:42.680 --> 34:45.480
Always playing
a different role to everyone,

34:46.640 --> 34:47.960
except it's not you.

34:54.600 --> 34:55.720
I have to go.

34:56.320 --> 34:57.160
Hey.

34:58.640 --> 34:59.480
Says who?

35:26.600 --> 35:27.840
-Ready?
-Huh?

35:28.760 --> 35:30.480
-Floor it.
-What?

35:30.560 --> 35:31.400
Floor it.

36:58.840 --> 36:59.680
Marly.

37:04.640 --> 37:05.960
