37:22.800 --> 37:24.160
-I…
-Leon.

37:27.920 --> 37:28.920
I've been thinking.

37:29.520 --> 37:31.480
-It's fine.
-No, it's not.

37:31.560 --> 37:35.840
It's not fair, how things have been going.
I've only been thinking of myself and--

37:35.920 --> 37:36.760
Leon.

37:36.840 --> 37:38.600
I did it. I left her.

37:40.400 --> 37:41.480
You did what?

37:42.320 --> 37:43.800
I just told her,

37:45.440 --> 37:46.400
"It's over."

37:46.480 --> 37:50.120
"I love someone else
and I want to start fresh with her."

37:52.400 --> 37:54.040
Marly, I love you.

38:08.240 --> 38:09.640
-Hello.
-<i>Hey, Frank.</i>

