Is he still alive?

38:54.880 --> 38:56.400
I was afraid to check.

39:00.640 --> 39:02.120
Oh, shit.

39:04.760 --> 39:05.840
Oh, fuck.

39:08.640 --> 39:11.280
Is he…

39:45.880 --> 39:47.120
