39:47.200 --> 39:49.400
Hey, I did all I could, okay?

39:49.480 --> 39:51.520
That guy knows how to drink,
for an alcoholic.

39:51.600 --> 39:53.840
This is a shame.
It'll cost us a lot of money.

39:57.240 --> 39:58.480
Holy shit.

39:58.560 --> 39:59.520
